casebody.data:
Linda A. BIRDETTE, petitioner,
v.
ASHWORTH COLLEGE, et al. No. 12-9285. Supreme Court of the United States May 20, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
